&lt;li&gt;Develop your team’s skills and careers, giving clear, actionable feedback and coaching toward greater scope and impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner deeply with Product and Engineering leaders to set strategy, plan effectively, and hit product and business metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold and elevate a high bar for design craft and usability across end-to-end experiences, from visual design to interaction details and animation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data and experimentation to inform decisions, measure outcomes, and iterate for impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with executives and our CEO in building excellent products.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion a creative, learner-first culture that balances bold bets with rigorous, data-driven improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
