&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering with PM and Engineering to define strategy, plan roadmaps, and deliver measurable results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, with the ability to articulate product rationale and design feedback clearly to executives and cross-functional partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong grasp of data-informed design; comfortable setting success metrics and reviewing experiments.&lt;/li&gt;
